quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,78,aur un ( ehley kitaab ) mein baze aisay hain ke kitaab ( torat ) ko zabaan maror maror kar parhte hain taakay tum samjhoo ke jo kuch woh parhte hain kitaab mein se hai halaank woh kitaab mein se nahi hai aur kehte hain ke woh khuda ki taraf se ( nazil howa ) hai halaank woh khuda ki taraf se nahi hota aur khuda par jhoot boltay hain aur ( yeh baat ) jantay bhi hain
  3,79,kisi aadmi ko Shayaan nahi ke khuda to usay kitaab aur hukoomat aur nabuwat ataa farmaiye aur woh logon se kahe ke khuda ko chore kar mere bande ho jao balkay ( is ko yeh kehna sazawar hai ke ae ehley kitaab ) tum ( ulmaye ) Rabbani ho jao kyunkay tum ktabِ ( khuda ) parhte parhatay rehtay ho
  3,80,aur is ko yeh bhi nahi kehna chahiye ke tum firshton aur payghambaroon ko khuda banalo bhala jab tum musalman ho chuke tokiya usay zaiba hai ke tumhe kafir honay ko kahe
  3,81,aur jab khuda ne payghambaroon se ehad liya ke jab mein tum ko kitaab aur danai ataa karoon phir tumahray paas koi paighambar aeye jo tumhari kitaab ki tasdeeq kere to tumhen zaroor is par imaan lana hoga aur zaroor is ki madad karni hogi aur ( ehad lainay ke baad ) poocha ke bhala tum ne iqraarkiya aur is iqraar par mera zimma liya ( yani mujhe zamin t_hraya ) unhon ne kaha ( haan ) hum ne iqraarkiya ( khuda ne ) farmaya ke tum ( is ehad o paymaan ke ) gawah raho aur mein bhi tumahray sath gawah hon
  3,82,to jo is ke baad phir jayen woh bad kirdaar hain
  3,83,kiya yeh ( kafir ) khuda ke deen ke siwa kisi aur deen ke taalib hain halaank sab ehley aasman o zameen khusi ya zabardasti se khuda ke farmaa bardaar hain aur isi ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
